title: Blind Taste Test Volume 1

description: On The Cigar Authority we begin the blind taste testing of cigars 1 vs 2, discuss the new Cigar Journal magazine and dodge swords at the Xing event..  Plus our regular segments, the Classic 3-Way, Inside the Asylum and Old Far Freddy.
